<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="title has-text-centered">
      <i class="fas fa-water" style="color: dodgerblue"></i>
      Oslob Whale Shark Watching
    </h1>
    <p class="subtitle has-text-centered">Discover and manage points of interest around the whale shark experience in Oslob, Cebu</p>

    <div class="columns is-multiline">
      <div class="column is-half">
        <div class="box">
          <h2 class="title is-4"><i class="fas fa-info-circle" style="color: dodgerblue"></i> About</h2>
          <p>The Oslob Whale Shark Watching is one of the most popular tourist attractions in the Philippines.
             Located in the small barangay of Tan-awan, visitors can swim and snorkel alongside gentle whale sharks
             (locally known as "butanding") in their natural habitat. The experience has drawn visitors from all over
             the world since 2011.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column is-half">
        <div class="box">
          <h2 class="title is-4"><i class="fas fa-clock" style="color: gold"></i> Opening Hours</h2>
          <p><strong>Daily:</strong> 6:00 AM – 12:00 PM</p>
          <p><strong>Best time to arrive:</strong> Before 7:00 AM</p>
          <p><strong>Note:</strong> Closed during severe weather conditions. Arrive early for the best experience as it
             can get busy during peak season (December – May).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column is-half">
        <div class="box">
          <h2 class="title is-4"><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt" style="color: crimson"></i> Location</h2>
          <p><strong>Address:</strong> Tan-awan, Oslob, Cebu, Philippines 6023</p>
          <p><strong>Coordinates:</strong> 9.4614°N, 123.3849°E</p>
          <p><strong>Getting there:</strong> Approximately 3–4 hours by bus from Cebu City South Bus Terminal.
             Private vans and tours are also available.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="column is-half">
        <div class="box">
          <h2 class="title is-4"><i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt" style="color: green"></i> This App</h2>
          <p>Use Placemark to discover, save and organise points of interest around the Oslob whale shark area.
             Create categories such as Beaches, Diving Spots, Waterfalls and Restaurants, then add placemarks
             with descriptions and GPS coordinates for each location.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>